Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF TOE BARRIO OF NUEVA COVETA, IN BURGOS, ILOCOS SUR, TO LUNA.
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 576, June 08, 1940 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF TOE BARRIO OF NUEVA COVETA, IN BURGOS, ILOCOS SUR, TO LUNA.
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of the barrio of Nueva Coveta, in the municipality of Burgos, Province of Ilocos Sur, is changed to Luna.ℒαwρhi৷
Section 2. This Act shall take effect on its approval.
Enacted, without Executive approval, June 8, 1940.
